I'm Jae  your dedicated Turo host. As a car enthusiast and avid traveler myself, I understand the importance of having the perfect vehicle for every journey. That's why I've curated a diverse fleet that caters to various preferences and needs.

Why Choose My Cars on Turo?

Quality and Maintenance:
Rest assured, each car in my fleet is meticulously maintained to ensure a smooth and worry-free ride. Your safety and comfort are my top priorities.

Diverse Selection:
From zippy compact cars for urban exploration to spacious SUVs for family road trips, my Turo fleet offers a variety of options. Find the perfect match for your unique travel style.

Personalized Service:
I believe in the personal touch. Need recommendations for local attractions, or want a special feature in the car for your journey? Just let me know, and I'll do my best to accommodate your requests.

Transparent Communication:
Communication is key. I'm here to answer any questions you may have and ensure a seamless Turo experience from booking to drop-off. Feel free to reach out at any time.

Convenient Pickup and Drop-off:
Forget about long lines and paperwork. Pick up and drop off your chosen vehicle at a location that suits you, whether it's the airport, your accommodation, or another agreed-upon spot.

Introducing Trap N Rentals NYC – Established in the heart of New York City, just moments away from LaGuardia Airport (LGA). Since 2020, our dedicated team, led by Sammie, works tirelessly to provide unparalleled service to our valued customers.

Trap N Rentals NYC offers a diverse fleet of vehicles, available for pickup or convenient delivery to your location within a 10-mile radius. Long-term rentals are our specialty, and Sammie is thrilled to offer exclusive discounts for extended bookings.

As a Turo-certified and Power * All Star Host, Trap N Rentals NYC takes pride in being the fastest-growing and top-rated host in the entire NYC area. With a fleet that’s constantly expanding, we guarantee a seamless rental experience, supported by 24/7 services and assistance.

Concerned about safety? Rest assured, all our vehicles undergo thorough daily disinfection to ensure a clean and secure environment for our customers. Additionally, Trap N Rentals NYC provides hassle-free contactless check-in and check-out options for both local and airport pickups, putting you behind the wheel in seconds.

Here are seven compelling reasons why Trap N Rentals NYC stands out:

	1.	Prime Location: Situated in the heart of NYC, we’re conveniently close to LGA, ensuring quick and easy access for our customers.
	2.	Instant Booking: Skip the wait – book instantly and drive off within minutes, with no lengthy paperwork or uncertainties.
	3.	Superior Customer Service: Expect the fastest, friendliest, and hassle-free car rental experience from our dedicated team.
	4.	Stellar Track Record: Join a community of satisfied customers with our consistently high 5-star reviews and exceptional feedback.
	5.	Well-Maintained Vehicles: Our fleet is meticulously cared for, ensuring each vehicle is clean and well-maintained inside and out.
	6.	Flexible Pickup and Delivery: Choose between picking up your vehicle at our location or opting for our convenient airport and local delivery services.
	7.	Extended Booking Options: Keep the car as long as you need, with flexible extensions as long as there are no conflicts with existing bookings.

At Trap N Rentals NYC, Sammie and the team are not just providing cars; they’re delivering an experience. Book 24/7, 365 days a year, and let our friendly, responsive team make your rental experience unforgettable. We look forward to hosting you in the city that never sleeps!
